  <title>WebKit2.Settings.media_playback_requires_user_gesture</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
Settings.media_playback_requires_user_gesture: Boolean (Read / Write / Construct)
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Whether a user gesture (such as clicking the play button)
would be required to start media playback or load media. This is off
by default, so media playback could start automatically.
Setting it on requires a gesture by the user to start playback, or to
load the media.</p>

